Phase 2 Completed: Database Setup & Deployment âœ…

The database layer has been fully initialized and deployed to uniCloud (Alibaba Cloud).

What has been completed:

âœ… Cloud database collections created

âœ… Database schemas defined and deployed

âœ… Initial test data inserted

âœ… Queries verified successfully in uniCloud console

Current collections:

Collection Name	Purpose
robots	Robot base information (robotCode, model, status)
telemetry_latest	Latest telemetry per robot (battery, position, online)
faults	Fault and error records
commands	Control command records (move / stop / goto)

This database structure simulates real robot telemetry and command flow, even before physical devices are available.